nhc_headline: ...NARDA STRENGTHENS SOME MORE WHILE REMAINING WELL TO THE SOUTH OF BAJA CALIFORNIA...
summary: ...NARDA STRENGTHENS SOME MORE WHILE REMAINING WELL TO THE SOUTH OF BAJA CALIFORNIA... As of 2:00 AM MST Wed Sep 24 the center of Narda was located near 15.1, -110.5 with movement W at 13 mph. The minimum central pressure was 970 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 105 mph.
